title: Don’t expect us to keep up the pace
author: VD
content_html:
But since the whole point was to enter this into the contest ending June 30th, Episode 3 of Midnight’s War, THE BLOOD MUST FLOW, is already live on Webtoons.

Still no word, however, on The Legend Chuck Dixon’s entry….
